article_title: Thousands set to lose WINhealth insurance
article_text:
Cheyenne, WY (82001)

Today

Showers possible.

Tonight

Cloudy with a few showers. Thunder possible. Low 42F. Winds N at 10 to 20 mph. Chance of rain 50%.

article_metadata.author: James Chilton

og.description: CHEYENNE - The recent announcement that WINhealth will pull out of Wyoming's health insurance marketplace next year means thousands of people will have to re-enroll for insurance.
